    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a dream. It\u2019s been pampered and kept in a garage its whole life, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s basically brand new. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
