    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative, collector-grade example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L atmospheric straight-six features individual throttle bodies and a documented VANOS overhaul, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is reached with surgical precision. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, with a chassis that has received comprehensive subframe reinforcement to exceed factory structural specifications. The exterior retains its original factory paint depth and luster, while the interior remains in a pristine state with no delamination of the soft-touch plastics or bolster wear on the Nappa leather. This vehicle represents a zero-compromise mechanical specimen with a complete service dossier and no deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
