    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, dealer-stamped service history documenting every scheduled maintenance and inspection. There are absolutely no leaks, rattles, or underlying issues. It comes complete with both original key fobs, all owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
